  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Core needle biopsy of orbital mass lesions with a semiautomated needles is a safe procedure
      that provides a sufficient amount of tissue material for standard histological and
      immunohistochemical analysis and can be an alternative or supplement to fine needle
      aspiration biopsy
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
